# Data Structures

### PromotionApplyType
+ applyType: `auto` (required, enum[string]) - Promotion apply-type (either coupon or automatic).
    + Members
        + `auto`
        + `coupon`

### Promotion
+ Include PromotionApplyType
+ form (required, PromotionForm) - Promotion form.
+ shadow (required, PromotionShadow) - Promotion shadow.

### PromotionIlluminated
+ id: 1 (required, number) - Promotion ID.
+ context: `default` (required, string) - Related context.
+ Include PromotionApplyType
+ attributes: `<json>` (required, string) - Promotion attributes.
+ discounts (required, array[DiscountIlluminated]) - Related illuminated discounts.

### PromotionForm
+ id: 1 (required, number) - Promotion form ID.
+ attributes: `<json>` (required, string) - Promotion form attributes.
+ createdAt: `2020-01-01T12:00:00Z` (required, string) - Creation date.

### PromotionAndDiscountForm
+ Include PromotionForm
+ discounts (required, array[DiscountForm]) - Related discount forms.

### PromotionShadow
+ id: 1 (required, number) - Promotion shadow ID.
+ formId: 1 (required, number) - Related promotion form ID.
+ attributes: `<json>` (required, string) - Promotion shadow attributes.
+ discounts (required, array[DiscountShadow]) - Related discount shadows.
+ createdAt: `2020-01-01T12:00:00Z` (required, string) - Creation date.

### DiscountForm
+ id: 1 (required, number) - Discount form ID.
+ attributes: `<json>` (required, string) - Discount form attributes.
+ createdAt: `2020-01-01T12:00:00Z` (required, string) - Creation date.

### DiscountShadow
+ id: 1 (required, number) - Discount shadow ID.
+ attributes: `<json>` (required, string) - Discount shadow attributes.
+ createdAt: `2020-01-01T12:00:00Z` (required, string) - Creation date.

### DiscountIlluminated
+ id: 1 (required, number) - Promotion form ID.
+ context: `default` (optional, string) - Related context.
+ attributes: `<json>` (required, string) - Promotion form attributes.

### CreatePromotionPayload
+ Include PromotionApplyType
+ form (required, CreatePromotionForm) - Promotion form.
+ shadow (required, CreatePromotionShadow) - Promotion shadow.

### CreatePromotionForm
+ attributes: `<json>` (required, string) - Promotion form attributes.
+ discounts (required, array[CreateDiscountForm]) - Promotion form discounts.

### CreatePromotionShadow
+ attributes: `<json>` (required, string) - Promotion shadow attributes.
+ discounts (required, array[CreateDiscountShadow]) - Promotion shadow discounts.

### CreateDiscountForm
+ attributes: `<json>` (required, string) - Discount form attributes.

### CreateDiscountShadow
+ attributes: `<json>` (required, string) - Discount shadow attributes.

### UpdatePromotionPayload
+ Include PromotionApplyType
+ form (required, UpdatePromotionForm) - Promotion form.
+ shadow (required, UpdatePromotionShadow) - Promotion shadow.

### UpdatePromotionForm
+ attributes: `<json>` (required, string) - Promotion form attributes.
